title: The Korzo Kovenant on #92Noon!
description: Scott Korzo is in for PA. What happened 42 years ago yesterday? Social issues in sports: the NCAA and student athletes, pride month, and the women's soccer team. The Star Tribune’s, Phil Miller, calls in to talk Twins. Just another reason MN is better than WI, we out-lake them. Jonny Athletic joins in studio to talk the Wolves, NBA, and of course, Vikings.
